Here's a simple P5.js sketch for a potential first draft of the nextbeststep.ai logo. This sketch creates a stylized arrow that can represent moving forward towards the next best step:

```javascript
function setup() {
  createCanvas(400, 400);
  angleMode(DEGREES);
}

function draw() {
  background(255);
  translate(width / 2, height / 2);

  fill(0, 128, 255);
  beginShape();
  vertex(-50, -50);
  vertex(50, -50);
  vertex(50, 0);
  vertex(100, 0);
  vertex(0, 100);
  vertex(-100, 0);
  vertex(-50, 0);
  endShape(CLOSE);
}
```

You can copy and paste this code into the P5.js web editor (https://editor.p5js.org/) to see the logo.

